  <section class="relative min-h-[50vh] flex items-center justify-center pt-20 overflow-hidden"><div class="absolute inset-0 z-0" style="background-image: url(&quot;https://horizons-cdn.hostinger.com/e3da7081-89fa-4296-8e0b-208ae94398b5/bda0fdb8b258bf205c0653b2583c1ec0.jpg&quot;); background-size: cover; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; transition: none; transform: none; animation: auto ease 0s 1 normal none running none;"></div><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/65 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/80 via-black/50 to-black/70 z-10 pointer-events-none"></div><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 relative z-20 text-center"><h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight drop-shadow-lg">Airport Taxi Service</h1><p class="text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-white/90 max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed drop-shadow-md">Reliable and comfortable airport transfers available 24/7. Professional drivers ensure you reach on time.</p></div></section><section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6"><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto"><h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Professional Airport Transfer Service</h2><p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">Our airport taxi service in Bangalore provides hassle-free transportation to and from Kempegowda International Airport. Whether you're arriving or departing, our professional drivers ensure a comfortable and timely journey.</p><div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 sm:gap-6"><div class="text-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="w-8 h-8 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 text-[#1E2D5A] mx-auto mb-3"><path d="M17.8 19.2 16 11l3.5-3.5C21 6 21.5 4 21 3c-1-.5-3 0-4.5 1.5L13 8 4.8 6.2c-.5-.1-.9.1-1.1.5l-.3